dc_title_s: Insurance maps of Trenton, New Jersey, volume three : including parts of Ewing Township
dc_description_s: Includes index key map, "New index, March, 1955" for streets, and legend. Includes record of insertion and correction dates 1957-69. Foot note: "This record supersedes similar record on individual sheets of this map". The updates were paste on the original sheet. "Copyright 1955". These maps were digitized from a copy held by the Trenton Free Public Library, housed in the Trentoniana Collection. Call number:  912.9 INSU
